{"tid":1876974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［捍衛攬炒］攬炒巴被老屈 你會放過","createTime":"2020-02-12T17:50:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T10:27:43.000Z","uid":193245,"like":35,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"870050f48eccfe34bcf23081d3efb64fc7a820fb","tid":1876974,"uid":193245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T17:50:24.000Z","msg":"事原係攬炒巴被老屈 <br />\n元兇就係<span style=\"color: orange;\"> 要求英國終止中英聯合聲明 </span>嘅 <span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>香港獨立黨</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成日屈「攬炒團隊」係「眾志」。我一直忍口唔屌出聲，屈撚完未呀？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1876737\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1876737</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n-----------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港獨立黨D人次次都將反共議題包裝到好靚，圖文並茂<br />\n然後再<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">陰陰濕濕喺個po嘅最尾攝一句<br />\n支持授權英國終止中英聯合聲明</span></strong> 永遠唔會開宗名義講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能攬炒團隊再三強調中英聯合聲明嘅重要性，不能廢除<br />\n然後就阻住hkip搵食，就<span style=\"color: violet;\">屈攬炒團隊做大台</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人一定一定一定要捍衛中英聯合聲明<br />\n因為中英聯合聲明係外國介入嘅最重要法理依據<br />\n冇論如何都唔可以廢除，一廢除咗就萬劫不復<br />\n萬一中英聯合聲明被廢除，攬炒團隊做幾多嘢都會被白費<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連登巴打，懇請大家唔好見到獨立兩個字就被沖昏頭腦<br />\n唔睇清楚就支持，會被立心不良嘅人騎劫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港獨立絕對唔係唯一一個選項<br />\n選項可以容後再傾<br />\n<br />\n無論如何<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">支持攬炒巴及攬炒團隊</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n另外，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港脱中 唯一出路</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"b0bca0dc09d9f58391693f4049e2b87f6b018075","tid":1876974,"uid":193245,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T17:53:03.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港脫中 唯一出路</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"92948d6193b69b0c5ec15767ffdab6d6747bdaae","tid":1876974,"uid":193245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T17:55:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>香港脫中 唯一出路</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"a378fe80efbfd4021dc91aa0b169ae1d97c640b4","tid":1876974,"uid":193245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T17:57:47.000Z","msg":"支持攬炒巴"},{"pid":"5ff300adaa1ceb142253239226e5f02f8dd69ed4","tid":1876974,"uid":346744,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T18:01:21.000Z","msg":"無知請教<br />\n<br />\n捍衛聯合聲明係想要捍衛中國主權唔獨立？<br />\n而家個政府無曬合法性喎確實<br />\n有可能終止到支那主權點解唔試？"},{"pid":"42ab74cfbc9e12238c608824eb5420894d7d5898","tid":1876974,"uid":193245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T18:05:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>支持攬炒團隊</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"c8bd7f8477a1c487a1a525fd5050c4990ebd1998","tid":1876974,"uid":193245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T18:07:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>光復香港 時代革命</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"ac4fd76a33aa70aa4e9316f0aa22b140eabdefb3","tid":1876974,"uid":193245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T18:08:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>光復香港 時代革命</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"0c95988a0bc8745c9fde8d12d47debfb0961c957","tid":1876974,"uid":76403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ff300adaa1ceb142253239226e5f02f8dd69ed4","tid":1876974,"uid":346744,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T18:01:21.000Z","msg":"無知請教<br />\n<br />\n捍衛聯合聲明係想要捍衛中國主權唔獨立？<br />\n而家個政府無曬合法性喎確實<br />\n有可能終止到支那主權點解唔試？"},"cit